        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7804_p1"> <note type="addendum" xml:id="K_7804_c0">Nachträglicher Stempel oben rechts mit von dritter Hand eingetragener Nummer: <orig>Gotthardbahn | <date when="1874-02-11">11 <choice><abbr>FEB.</abbr><expan>FEBRUAR</expan></choice> 1874</date>. | <choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice> 640.</orig>
            – Nachträgliche Inhaltsangabe oben links von dritter Hand: <orig>Vorlage einer neuen Procuration
              <choice><abbr>betr.</abbr><expan>betreffend</expan></choice> den Herrn <persName key="Brandner Henri">Henri Brandner</persName>. | I <choice><abbr>Depart.</abbr><expan>Departement</expan></choice> </orig> – Nachträgliche Notiz unten links von Eschers Hand mit Bleistift: <orig><choice><abbr>N. B.</abbr><expan>Nota Bene (beachte)</expan></choice> | Die Generalvollmachten
                    sind bei den Originalurkunden
                    aufzubewahren.</orig> – Nachträgliche  Notiz unten in der Mitte von dritter Hand: <orig><choice><abbr>Prot.</abbr><expan>Protokoll</expan></choice> <date when="1876-02-05">5. II. 76</date>. <choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> 194</orig>.</note> <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <hi rend="printed">ENTREPRISE <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>DU
            <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>TUNNEL DU <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">GOTHARD</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>L. FAVRE &amp; <choice><abbr>C<hi rend="sup">IE</hi> </abbr><expan>COMPAGNIE (Gesellschaft)</expan></choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/><choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice></hi> 62</p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7804_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>
          <hi rend="printed">
            <placeName key="Altdorf (UR)">Altorf</placeName> (Canton d'<placeName key="Uri">Uri</placeName>-Suisse), le</hi>
          <date when="1874-02-01">1<hi rend="sup">er</hi> Février <hi rend="printed">187</hi>4</date>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7804_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>Monsieur Escher, Président du Comité de
        <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>Direction du Chemin de fer du Gothard,</p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7804_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>à <placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7804_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>Monsieur Le Président,</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7804_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>Nous avons l'honneur de vous remettre,
        <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>ci-joint, une nouvelle procuration au nom
            <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>de <choice><abbr>M.</abbr><expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan></choice> <persName key="Brandner Henri">Henri Brandner</persName>, modifiée selon les
        <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>prescriptions de votre lettre du <date when="1874-01-21">21</date>/<date when="1874-01-24">24 janvier<note type="transcript">sic!</note> <choice><abbr>d<hi rend="sup">er</hi></abbr><expan>dernier (letzter)</expan></choice>.</date> </p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7804_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>Veuillez agréer, Monsieur Le Président,
        <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>l'assurance de nos sentiments respectueux,</p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7804_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>
          <choice><abbr>pp<hi rend="sup">on</hi> </abbr><expan>par procuration (stellvertretend für)</expan></choice><note type="transcript">par procuration</note> <persName key="Favre Louis">L Favre</persName>:
        <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/><persName key="Brandner Henri">H. Brandner</persName> </p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>